Text:
You should only need a KeyCD after upgrading, if you are upgrading a MK.III BMW Navigation computer running V.15 to V.17 software version. Higher than V.17 shouldn't need this CD.

See this Torrent for more information: 

http://thepiratebay.org/tor/3644012/BMW_Navigation_System_FAQ

See the above Torrent for information how to identify which BMW Navigator you have, which version it is on, and how far you can upgrade it, and which new freatures you will get.

See my other torrents for different KeyCD images for different software. 

Record the KeyCD at low speed 2XA as the Navigator might not read other formats for the KeyCD.
